          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p rend="align(center)">
                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="align(center)indent(1)">
                                        <date>Feby 13<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1849</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Dr Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">To prevent my not having the<lb/> pleasure to meet
                                        you not having but one day to<lb/> remain in
                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> en route I
                                        thought I<lb/> would thus name to you that I shall call
                                        on<lb/> you by <date>10 on Thursday at 3 Oclock PM</date> I
                                        intend<lb/> arriving in your city on <date>Wednesday at 10
                                                  PM</date> making<lb/> my home at the Madison house
                                        I have met<lb/>
                                        <persName>Drs Wise &amp; Lilienthal</persName> and with them
                                        and our<lb/> friend <persName>Mr I Lindo</persName> have
                                        composed a circular<lb/> bringing to the public notice the
                                        final propositions<lb/> for the convention of Jews in
                                                  <placeName>Phila.</placeName> more anon<lb/> in
                                        the interim let me call to your notice a small<lb/>
                                        paragraph in this days Herald which fully<lb/> expresses our
                                        views how it found its entrance<lb/> their I know not
                                        commending you to the<lb/> care of mutual protector</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">I am truly Yours</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">
                                        <persName role="author">Lewis Abraham</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>My father in law <persName>Mr E Mayer</persName> who accompanies
                                        me<lb/> will wait on you with me</p>
                    </body>
